  "text": "PVE strongly depends on the size of the tumor. The smaller the tumor, the greater the underestimation of the uptake value. As a result, different tumors with exactly the same uptake value but with different sizes yield tumor images with different degrees of brightness and hence different estimated uptake values (Fig. 5) [CITATION_1] .",
